<td colspan="2" style="text-align:center"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/bishop/bratz.html"><small><span class="indicateur-langue">(<abbr class="abbr" title="Langue&#160;: anglais">en</abbr>)</span> Notice sur <i>www.catholic-hierarchy.org</i></small></a></td>
