e_de_Tr%C3%A8ves" title="Diocèse de Trèves">Trèves</a></i>&#160;: <a href="/wiki/Stephan_Ackermann" title="Stephan Ackermann">Stephan Ackermann</a> <span style="font-weight:bold">·</span></span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Robert_Brahm" title="Robert Brahm">Robert Brahm</a> (<abbr class="abbr" title="évêque auxiliaire">aux.</abbr>) <span style="font-weight:bold">·</span></span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Helmut_Dieser" title="Helmut Dieser">Helmut Dieser</a> (<abbr class="abbr" title="évêque auxiliaire">aux.</abbr>) <span style="font-weight:bold">·</span></span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/J%C3%B6rg_Michael_Peters" title="Jörg Michael Peters">Jörg Michael Peters</a> (<abbr class="abbr" title="évêque auxiliaire">aux.</abbr>)</span></td>
